@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wanlwe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.78
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.24) - (v0 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.53)) - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.17) + (v1 + 0.20 + v0 + 0.54)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.93)) + (0.31 * (tmp + 0.10 / v1 + 0.43)))
    tmp = ((tmp - (v1 + 0.38 * tmp + 0.14)) - v0)
    v1 = v0
    v0 = 0.89
    data[tid] = v0
